  m_text: 'We have not yet seen any complications from this virus.

    We are however
    aware of the following symptoms


    Arm Rash OR Back Acne OR Chest Discolouration
    \nAcne and Chest Discolouration NOT considered if both apparent at the same time
    \n Rapid Weight Loss\n Irregular Speech'
