  m_text: 'All citizens must remain at home whilst they await instructions on how
    they are evacuated.

    A number of citizens will be evacuated each day and
    will be tested, and then inspected at border control for symptoms to be allowed
    through.


    Additional protective forces are surrounding the dome to ensure
    external governments cannot make use of this situation to their advantage.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
